    [127569] = [[This stag is found outside the zone barrier, so cannot be physically reached. Instead, in a couple of places around the edge you can just get in range to aggro it with something that won't kill it, like a Tar Trap, which will in turn cause it to come close enough to tame. Invasion Point: Bonich may be reached through a portal in northern Antoran Wastes, Argus.]],
