    [162588] = [[Gristlebeak cannot initially be attacked, but circles an area east of the the Theater of Pain. She will descend and attack if you destroy her clutch of Unusual Eggs, found further east the foot of jagged, blackened peaks.]],
    [162681] = [[Normally friendly but can be tamed if you use the toy "N'lyeth, Sliver of N'Zoth" while in War Mode. The Elusive Quickhoof is an alpaca that spawns rarely and can be found wandering in one of many different locations in Vol'dun. If you feed it some Seaside Leafy Greens Mix it will award you the Elusive Quickhoof mount. It's still possible to tame it afterwards, as the alpaca remains up for 10 minutes after spawning.]],
    [163025] = [[Appears in the Assaults phase of the zone. Respawns frequently, not far inside the eastern entrance to the Obelisk of the Moon and immediately runs towards the entrance. Tame it as soon as it spawns, before the other NPCs attack and steal threat.]],
    [163042] = [[Normally friendly, but can be tamed if you use the toy "N'lyeth, Sliver of N'Zoth" while in War Mode. The Ivory Cloud Serpent appears only during Mogu Assaults. The Ivory Cloud Serpent spawns every ~1.5 - 3 hours at coordinates ~ 27,55, at roughly 2-3 times the height of the trees, and flies rapidly in clockwise circuits around the zone. The best place to tame it is at the southern end of the roof of the Gate of the Setting Sun.]],
    [163045] = [[This untameable version of the Aqir Stinger is found only around the Obelisk of the Moon, during all Assaults phases.]],
