    [212040] = [[There's a chance this beast will appear when you use an Elusive Creature Bait in the Emerald Dream zone of the Dragon Isles. To create Elusive Creature Bait you must have levelled Dragon Isles Skinning to the point where you can select the Bait Crafter specialization (see your skinning journal inside your professions panel) and spend at least 10 points of Knowledge in it.]],
