    [219654] = [[Located in Dalaran (Khaz Algar intro quest phase). Only appears during the Breach intro quest for The War Within, when Dalaran first arrives at the Isle of Dorn and is under siege. Flies high, so you'll need to find a suitable location and possibly shoot it to bring it into taming range. Only the black and the green variants make sounds when clicked.]],
